Troubleshooting Tips
Issue 1: MobSF Server Won't Start
Symptoms: Error messages when running manage.py runserver

Solutions:

# Check if port 8000 is already in use
sudo netstat -tulpn | grep 8000

# Kill existing process if needed
sudo kill -9 <PID>

# Check Python dependencies
pip3 install -r requirements.txt

# Verify Java installation
java -version
Issue 2: API Authentication Fails
Symptoms: 401 Unauthorized errors when using API

Solutions:

Verify API key is correct in script
Check header format: {"Authorization": "your_api_key"}
Ensure API key hasn't expired
Try regenerating API key
Issue 3: Analysis Takes Too Long
Symptoms: APK analysis doesn't complete

Solutions:

Check APK file size (large files take longer)
Verify sufficient disk space: df -h
Monitor MobSF logs: tail -f logs/mobsf.log
Restart MobSF server if hung
Issue 4: Python Script Import Errors
Symptoms: ModuleNotFoundError when running scripts

Solutions:

# Install missing modules
pip3 install requests

# Verify Python path
echo $PYTHONPATH

# Run with explicit Python 3
python3 script.py
